   <location num='516' flags='a'>
      <name>Frontier Gunsmiths</name>
      <desc>   This gunsmiths may be small, but it is most comprehensively stocked, with weapons of all different kinds, many of which appear to be of alien manufacture.</desc>
      <desc>   Of particular interest is the fine display of missiles along one wall.</desc>
      <desc>   The exit is east.</desc>
      <exits e='517' out='517' no-exit='moves.noexit.3'/>
   </location>

   <location num='517'>
      <name>City street</name>
      <desc>   You are standing at the south end of one of the city&apos;s main roads. A road leads south, to the Mars landing area. There is a building to the west, and a small dirt track leads off to the southeast.</desc>
      <exits n='453' se='582' s='581' w='516' in='516'/>
   </location>

   <location num='521'>
      <name>Street</name>
      <desc>   The street comes to an abrupt stop here as it reaches a dead end. All around you are tall, featureless buildings.</desc>
      <desc>   Northwest, the street leads back to a complex of warehouses. There is a door to the south.</desc>
      <exits s='585' nw='456' in='585'/>
   </location>

   <location num='524'>
      <name>Sacrifice</name>
      <desc>You start to walk down the dark steps...</desc>
      <exits up='271' out='271'/>
      <events in-room='death.ruins.3'/>
   </location>

   <location num='527' flags='t'>
      <name>Courtyard</name>
      <desc>   This small courtyard is entirely surrounded by high walls. Touching the surface of the walls, you realize they would be impossible to climb because whatever substance they are made from feels very slippery.</desc>
      <desc>   The courtyard continues to the east, and there is a small gap to the south.</desc>
      <exits e='528' s='591' no-exit='moves.noexit.1'/>
   </location>

   <location num='528' flags='t'>
      <name>Courtyard</name>
      <desc>   The high walls around this courtyard cut you off from the outside completely.</desc>
      <desc>   In the center of the courtyard is a matt black pillar surrounded by the bones of creatures - some unknown, others only too recognizable as human skeletons.</desc>
      <desc>   In one corner of the courtyard is a heap of rubble. A glint of metal amongst the rocks indicates there might be something interesting concealed there.</desc>
      <exits w='527' out='527' no-exit='moves.noexit.1'/>
      <vocab cmd='search' event='objects.artifacts.1'/>
   </location>

   <location num='530' flags='t'>
