   <location num='579'>
      <name>Toboggan</name>
      <desc>   The toboggan is huge, both long and wide, providing room for many passengers. Like the hopper it has replaced for Christmas, it has been provided by Diesel and it it moves between the bar and Marsport on a regular schedule, whether there are any passengers or not.</desc>
      <desc>   The benches are covered with fur, to provide warmth in the cold snow outside the toboggan. A metal bar will snap into place to prevent anybody from falling off the toboggan.</desc>
      <exits out='773'/>
   </location>

   <location num='581'>
